{
  "stem": "19111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 241.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I recall the Russians used to have big screen movies out in the streets and call the-- the people, population to see.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all you saw was, the-- they were showing the revolution of 1917, and explaining what has transpired, and tell them where-- that the future is so great, and all that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We still had enough to eat, and to-- and to enjoy life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The synagogue was really-- the synagogues were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we did not attend anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a way, it was sort of like we were a little afraid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the NKVD at that time, they kept records of who is what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't want to rock the boat, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And did the Betar stop?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, actually, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They continued a little bit more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were, it's a matter of fact, at the time when the Russians occupied Vilna in 1939, the-- the other part of Poland that was occupied by Germany, and they began to suffer all the indignations and all the-- the hardships and the-- and the slaughter, a lot of-- quite a few of those had managed to come to Vilna, the-- especially young boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They managed to run away from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they formed the [NON-ENGLISH] groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were transient in Vilna who with a-- with a-- a hope to reach Israel or Palestine at the time, any given time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they wanted to go to Palestine to work and build, and I guess fight for an independent country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so they were transients and they were in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was rather very difficult for them to get out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the meantime, they did all kinds of menial works there, to support themselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
